Subject: drm/amd/powerplay: apply clocks adjust rules on power state change
Git-commit: e17c7f92b2b7c2f14934c305a8d72bbb0bf6f362
Patch-mainline: v4.19-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

This add the apply_clocks_adjust_rules callback which is used
to validate the clock settings on a power state change.

